# The lack of output from the movement command suggests that the action to move to the nearest stone resource did not yield a visible result.
# I will directly attempt to harvest stone from the nearest resource without waiting for confirmation of movement.

# Harvesting stone from the nearest stone resource
harvested_stone_quantity = harvest_resource(nearest(Resource.Stone), quantity=10)  # Attempting to collect 10 stone.
print(f"Inventory changed to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Displaying the updated inventory after harvesting stone.
